HEADWORD: Lingism
<hw>Ling"ism</hw> <pr>(l⟦icr⟧ng"⟦icr⟧z'm)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A
mode of treating certain diseases, as obesity, by gymnastics; --
proposed by <person>Pehr Henrik <etsep>Ling</etsep></person>, a Swede.
See <er>Kinesiatrics</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

